  <figure class="container-prose post-hero">
    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-6-2025-02_37_50-AM.png" alt="How to Make an Offer on a House: Winning in Competitive Markets" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
